<div id="intro">
  <p>Learn how to write truly concurrent programs&mdash;programs that run on dozens or even hundreds of local and remote processors. See how to write high reliability applications&mdash;even in the face of network and hardware failure&mdash;using the Erlang programming language.</p>
  
  
</div>


